cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Memory Arena in research or a public writeup, please cite both this software and the underlying LongMemEval corpus."
title: "Memory Arena: Apples-to-apples benchmark for agent-memory architectures"
abstract: >-
  Memory Arena benchmarks 21 agent-memory architectures (Mem0, Mem0+Graph,
  Graphiti, Graphiti-on-FalkorDB, Cognee, LangMem, Memori, A-MEM, HippoRAG 2,
  Karpathy LLM Wiki, the quantum rerankers QISS and SQR, plus pure-Python
  baselines and advanced retrievers like HyDE, RAPTOR, Reflection, Persona
  Profile, Hybrid RRF) on the same chat-session corpus, scored by the same
  evaluator, under the same configs.
authors:
  - family-names: Puspus
    given-names: Xavier
    email: xpuspus@gmail.com
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/xmpuspus/memory-arena"
url: "https://github.com/xmpuspus/memory-arena"
